38
00:02:04,370 --> 00:02:06,150
the same day Master Pi passed away.

39
00:02:06,890 --> 00:02:08,350
After the comet appeared,

40
00:02:08,730 --> 00:02:10,710
I started hearing a voice in my head.

41
00:02:11,530 --> 00:02:13,450
I thought it was just

42
