a mental issue,

43
00:02:15,850 --> 00:02:16,930
but the more time I spent

44
00:02:16,930 --> 00:02:18,630
with Fang Meng,

45
00:02:18,890 --> 00:02:20,050
the more frequent

46
00:02:20,050 --> 00:02:21,230
