00:15:39,050 --> 00:15:40,150
Meng, don't cry.

289
00:15:41,050 --> 00:15:41,950
Don't cry.

290
00:15:51,210 --> 00:15:52,790
Based on what I know about her,

291
00:15:53,170 --> 00:15:54,510
she won't blame you.

292
00:15:55,490 --> 00:15:57,110
It's my own arrogance that caused this.

293
00:15:57,690 --> 00:15:58,910
We never expected things

294
00:15:59,130 --> 00:16:00,310
to turn out this way,

295
00:16:01,090 --> 00:16:02,230
so we'll just have to accept it.

296
00:16:03,850 --> 00:16:05,390
Hua Su is your life's work.

297
00:16:06,050 --> 00:16:07,550
She feels like

298
00:16:07,770 --> 00:16:10,070
she's ruined the brand you built.

299
00:16:11,210 --> 00:16:12,910
After today,

300
00:16:13,570 --> 00:16:15,070
she probably
won't want to cook anymore.

301
00:16:18,370 --> 00:16:19,390
In the past,

302
00:16:19,970 --> 00:16:21,370
I always stopped her

303
00:16:21,370 --> 00:16:22,350
from cooking,

304
00:16:23,610 --> 00:16:24,630
but now,

305
00:16:25,130 --> 00:16:27,230
I hope she keeps going.

306
00:16:28,730 --> 00:16:30,510
Honestly, with those six dishes,

307
00:16:30,770 --> 00:16:32,430
if the people on the street
had tasted them,

308
00:16:32,850 --> 00:16:34,470
no one would have thought
there was any foul play.

309
00:16:36,010 --> 00:16:36,950
It's a shame

310
00:16:37,370 --> 00:16:38,390
no one believes her now.

311
00:16:38,930 --> 00:16:41,150
It's not about whether
others believe her anymore,

312
00:16:41,890 --> 00:16:44,070
it's that Fang Meng
no longer believes in herself.

313
00:16:51,810 --> 00:16:53,430
Tell me, what happened.

314
00:16:56,090 --> 00:16:57,910
Lin Chuxiao, I'm asking you.

315
00:16:58,610 --> 00:17:00,790
Shouldn't I ask you that?

316
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:02,160
What if An Zhijiang

317
00:17:02,170 --> 00:17:03,550
sees you barging in like this?

318
00:17:03,810 --> 00:17:05,030
Are you afraid of him this much?

319
00:17:09,010 --> 00:17:10,310
Just tell me what it is.

320
00:17:15,770 --> 00:17:16,610
Answer me,

321
00:17:16,850 --> 00:17:18,830
did you bring people
to tear down Hua Su yesterday?

322
00:17:20,770 --> 00:17:23,070
Let's talk about it at home, okay?

323
00:17:24,490 --> 00:17:25,550
Lin Chuxiao,

324
00:17:25,690 --> 00:17:26,710
good for you.

325
00:17:26,970 --> 00:17:28,510
You're acting like you're someone else.

326
00:17:29,010 --> 00:17:29,850
Fine,

327
00:17:29,890 --> 00:17:31,510
even if you don't
treat Fang Meng as a friend,

328
00:17:31,690 --> 00:17:33,250
what about Shu Zhengyan?

329
00:17:33,250 --> 00:17:34,470
Can you face him?

330
00:17:41,620 --> 00:17:44,380
(Bo Fei Group)

331
00:17:46,050 --> 00:17:47,430
Why don't you tell me

332
00:17:49,010 --> 00:17:51,030
what should I do from my position?

333
00:17:51,890 --> 00:17:52,730
Your position?

334
00:17:53,300 --> 00:17:54,610
As soon as An Zhijiang
took his position,

335
00:17:54,610 --> 00:17:56,110
your position changed, right?

336
00:18:00,890 --> 00:18:02,750
Now I don't want to talk about this,

337
00:18:03,490 --> 00:18:04,330
I'm busy.

338
00:18:05,370 --> 00:18:06,950
I know why you're doing this.

339
00:18:07,170 --> 00:18:08,050
Everything you do

340
00:18:08,050 --> 00:18:09,550
is for your own job.

341
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:12,070
You've betrayed Shu Zhengyan,

342
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:13,390
you've betrayed Fang Meng,

343
00:18:14,330 --> 00:18:15,270
you've betrayed me.

344
00:18:17,330 --> 00:18:18,170
Betray?

345
00:18:20,210 --> 00:18:21,490
None of the things I'm doing

346
00:18:21,490 --> 00:18:22,830
is beyond my responsibilities.

347
00:18:27,330 --> 00:18:28,170
Yes,

348
00:18:28,530 --> 00:18:29,630
you guys are happy.

349
00:18:29,850 --> 00:18:31,190
You guys have a good father,

350
00:18:32,290 --> 00:18:34,310
you can do whatever you like.

351
00:18:34,930 --> 00:18:35,770
What about me?

352
00:18:37,050 --> 00:18:38,790
I got this decent job.

353
00:18:39,570 --> 00:18:40,990
Are you telling me to just give it up?

354
00:18:42,370 --> 00:18:43,210
Miss Princess,

355
00:18:43,770 --> 00:18:46,630
do you know how hard it is
to find a decent job?

356
00:18:47,410 --> 00:18:49,810
Do you expect me
to be like Shu Zhengyan,

357
00:18:49,810 --> 00:18:51,990
running errands at Hua Su every day,

358
00:18:52,370 --> 00:18:53,790
just to be loyal?

359
00:18:54,530 --> 00:18:56,150
I've told him so many times

360
00:18:56,570 --> 00:18:57,770
not to bother with Hua Su,

361
00:18:57,770 --> 00:18:58,950
not to care about Fang Meng.

362
00:18:59,610 --> 00:19:00,790
Did he listen?

363
00:19:01,760 --> 00:19:03,550
Did I do this for me?

364
00:19:05,250 --> 00:19:06,310
Why don't you tell me

365
00:19:07,380 --> 00:19:09,190
without this job,

366
00:19:09,330 --> 00:19:10,670
how can I marry you?

367
00:19:12,690 --> 00:19:13,670
Decency?

368
00:19:14,520 --> 00:19:15,410
Decency.

369
00:19:15,410 --> 00:19:17,710
You're talking about decency now?

370
00:19:18,370 --> 00:19:20,270
So An Zhijiang gave you decency?

371
00:19:22,870 --> 00:19:24,070
I'm telling you,

372
00:19:24,550 --> 00:19:26,390
you don't need this decency,

373
00:19:27,560 --> 00:19:29,230
and I don't need you to marry me.

374
00:20:44,730 --> 00:20:45,710
What are you doing here?

375
00:20:47,690 --> 00:20:48,630
You woke up?

376
00:20:50,130 --> 00:20:52,110
I saw the door wasn't locked,
so I came in.

377
00:21:00,690 --> 00:21:02,430
This place is so old.

378
00:21:04,210 --> 00:21:05,350
Maybe it's time to move.

379
00:21:06,450 --> 00:21:07,630
A new place

380
00:21:08,090 --> 00:21:10,150
might bring new moods.

381
00:21:13,050 --> 00:21:14,910
When one road is blocked,

382
00:21:15,850 --> 00:21:17,430
you have to change paths.

383
00:21:18,410 --> 00:21:20,250
I loved cooking back then,

384
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:22,510
so I kept pushing myself

385
00:21:23,130 --> 00:21:24,550
to take different ratings and exams.

386
00:21:25,290 --> 00:21:27,510
But over time,

387
00:21:28,450 --> 00:21:29,830
cooking started to feel

388
00:21:30,330 --> 00:21:32,230
like another kind of exam.

389
00:21:33,210 --> 00:21:34,390
Now I see,

390
00:21:35,010 --> 00:21:36,110
I was wrong.

391
00:21:36,410 --> 00:21:38,950
Back then, I was so sure that

392
00:21:40,210 --> 00:21:41,590
your dad's path wasn't working.

393
00:21:41,930 --> 00:21:43,670
I thought Hua Su would close one day.

394
00:21:47,610 --> 00:21:48,790
You weren't wrong.

395
00:21:50,370 --> 00:21:52,230
It's true that this happened.

396
00:21:56,650 --> 00:21:58,070
I didn't mean that.

397
00:22:00,530 --> 00:22:01,370
When your dad was around,

398
00:22:01,370 --> 00:22:02,670
Hua Su was always doing well.

399
00:22:04,850 --> 00:22:06,670
What's the point
of talking about this now?

400
00:22:08,730 --> 00:22:09,990
Hua Su is gone.

401
00:22:13,770 --> 00:22:16,230
I didn't believe in your dad back then,

402
00:22:17,010 --> 00:22:17,990
but now,

403
00:22:18,690 --> 00:22:19,790
I believe in you.

404
00:22:22,570 --> 00:22:24,710
When did you come in?

405
00:22:25,450 --> 00:22:26,870
Just now.

406
00:22:27,050 --> 00:22:27,890
Just now.

407
00:22:29,490 --> 00:22:30,670
Did you hear everything?

408
00:22:31,210 --> 00:22:32,430
I didn't hear it all.

409
00:22:34,090 --> 00:22:34,930
Fang Meng.

410
00:22:35,370 --> 00:22:37,670
This is my fault.

411
00:22:38,090 --> 00:22:39,710
I shouldn't have agreed
to sign the contract.

412
00:22:40,370 --> 00:22:41,310
I'm not blaming you.

413
00:22:42,850 --> 00:22:44,270
I think your mom is right.

414
00:22:44,770 --> 00:22:46,110
At worst, we can start over.

415
00:22:46,570 --> 00:22:48,550
Plus, you've already learned
six signature dishes.

416
00:22:48,890 --> 00:22:50,910
I believe you'll do better
and better in the future.

417
00:22:53,730 --> 00:22:55,110
Did he hear that?

418
00:22:59,010 --> 00:23:01,150
You know, you were wrong
not to trust me, right?

419
00:23:02,290 --> 00:23:04,550
Starting over isn't that simple.

420
00:23:05,810 --> 00:23:07,190
Now I don't even have a restaurant.

421
00:23:09,890 --> 00:23:11,190
I'll find you one.

422
00:23:12,210 --> 00:23:13,750
The good locations I could have found

423
00:23:14,250 --> 00:23:15,810
are either bought by Bo Fei Group

424
00:23:15,810 --> 00:23:17,230
or already taken.

425
00:23:17,810 --> 00:23:18,830
How can you find a place now?

426
00:23:19,450 --> 00:23:21,510
Although I'm not the president anymore,

427
00:23:23,210 --> 00:23:24,550
I still have resources.

428
00:23:24,630 --> 00:23:25,490
Believe me,

429
00:23:25,490 --> 00:23:27,030
I'll find a good location for you.

430
00:23:29,660 --> 00:23:32,940
(Today Happy, Day Day Happy)

431
00:23:37,930 --> 00:23:39,670
This is the place you found?

432
00:23:42,770 --> 00:23:44,150
It doesn't matter where the place is.

433
00:23:44,320 --> 00:23:45,800
As long as we cook good food,

434
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:47,830
we'll have customers wherever we open.

435
00:23:48,370 --> 00:23:49,230
Besides,

436
00:23:49,370 --> 00:23:51,650
Bo Fei Group only bought our shop,

437
00:23:51,650 --> 00:23:52,870
not our brand.

438
00:23:52,970 --> 00:23:54,590
So we can still use the name Hua Su.

439
00:23:55,370 --> 00:23:56,310
Seriously?

440
00:23:58,490 --> 00:23:59,330
Meng.

441
00:24:00,570 --> 00:24:01,930
I have a meeting today,

442
00:24:01,930 --> 00:24:02,950
so I'm leaving.

443
00:24:04,290 --> 00:24:05,550
You do your best.

444
00:24:13,390 --> 00:24:16,150
I feel like she still doesn't believe me.

445
00:24:17,290 --> 00:24:18,230
Not only your mom,

446
00:24:18,450 --> 00:24:19,510
I don't believe you either.

447
00:24:21,330 --> 00:24:22,510
We trust you.

448
00:24:25,730 --> 00:24:26,630
What do you mean "we"?

449
00:24:30,130 --> 00:24:31,190
I trust you.

450
00:24:32,410 --> 00:24:33,270
I've decided,

451
00:24:33,930 --> 00:24:34,910
from today on,

452
00:24:35,120 --> 00:24:37,510
I'll make Hua Su bigger and stronger.

453
00:24:37,730 --> 00:24:39,070
Do you have confidence?

454
00:24:44,450 --> 00:24:45,470
Alright, Fang Meng,

455
00:24:46,170 --> 00:24:47,010
don't worry.

456
00:24:47,730 --> 00:24:48,570
I'm here,

457
00:24:49,370 --> 00:24:50,210
Dazui is here,

458
00:24:50,890 --> 00:24:51,910
we are all with you.

459
00:24:52,770 --> 00:24:53,750
Everything will be fine.

460
00:24:58,940 --> 00:25:01,980
(Jiangnan University
Affiliated Hospital)

461
00:25:13,210 --> 00:25:14,870
He is still resting.

462
00:25:15,250 --> 00:25:16,510
Should we leave now?

463
00:25:23,570 --> 00:25:24,950
Dad, you're awake.

464
00:25:27,170 --> 00:25:28,150
This is Fang Meng.

465
00:25:29,570 --> 00:25:30,410
Hello, Uncle.

466
00:25:34,210 --> 00:25:35,430
You're Fang Meng?

467
00:25:36,970 --> 00:25:37,810
Zhengyan,

468
00:25:38,370 --> 00:25:39,870
let me say a few words to her.

469
00:25:42,450 --> 00:25:43,730
Dad, it's so late.

470
00:25:43,730 --> 00:25:44,710
Just two words.

471
00:25:51,690 --> 00:25:54,030
If he wants to eat a lollipop, tell me.

472
00:26:07,610 --> 00:26:08,470
Fang Meng,

473
00:26:10,250 --> 00:26:11,090
do you know that

474
00:26:11,090 --> 00:26:13,510
you're not fit to be a chef?

475
00:26:16,490 --> 00:26:18,090
Look at what you've done

476
00:26:18,090 --> 00:26:19,710
to your father's restaurant.

477
00:26:21,770 --> 00:26:23,390
Uncle, you might not know, but

478
00:26:23,590 --> 00:26:24,690
I've already chosen a new location

479
00:26:24,690 --> 00:26:26,160
for Hua Su.

480
00:26:26,160 --> 00:26:27,470
If you have time,
you can come try the food.

481
00:26:27,470 --> 00:26:28,490
I've heard that your Hua Su

482
00:26:28,490 --> 00:26:30,350
has scared many people away.

483
00:26:30,490 --> 00:26:32,070
Which street did you choose?

484
00:26:32,290 --> 00:26:33,670
Should I hide from it?

485
00:26:34,580 --> 00:26:35,740
That was in the past.

486
00:26:35,740 --> 00:26:37,020
Now I've learned

487
00:26:37,020 --> 00:26:38,620
my father's six signature dishes.

488
00:26:38,620 --> 00:26:40,480
People won't be running away
after eating them. Don't worry.

489
00:26:41,380 --> 00:26:43,380
You're still imitating your father.

490
00:26:46,900 --> 00:26:47,740
Please, sit down.

491
00:26:56,260 --> 00:26:57,100
Fang Meng,

492
00:26:57,380 --> 00:26:58,580
do you know that

493
00:26:59,740 --> 00:27:01,580
cooking is like

494
00:27:01,980 --> 00:27:03,420
painting a picture,

495
00:27:03,980 --> 00:27:06,220
writing a poem, or playing music?

496
00:27:06,940 --> 00:27:08,620
It takes talent.

497
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:13,220
I know,

498
00:27:15,140 --> 00:27:17,140
because my father often said so.

499
00:27:17,740 --> 00:27:19,180
He said I didn't have talent

500
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:20,740
and wasn't suited to be a chef.

501
00:27:21,100 --> 00:27:22,820
He never taught me to cook.

502
00:27:25,500 --> 00:27:27,380
But actually, he's tasted

503
00:27:27,380 --> 00:27:28,740
every dish I cooked.

504
00:27:30,300 --> 00:27:32,180
He thought he was keeping it a secret,

505
00:27:33,300 --> 00:27:35,500
but I just knew it.

506
00:27:36,940 --> 00:27:38,540
But if it weren't for those times,

507
00:27:38,540 --> 00:27:40,460
I wouldn't have kept going.

508
00:27:44,060 --> 00:27:45,460
Not to mention

509
00:27:46,180 --> 00:27:47,580
I don't even have a shop now.

510
00:27:49,260 --> 00:27:50,300
But I know

511
00:27:52,420 --> 00:27:53,580
he's always been there for me.

512
00:27:57,020 --> 00:27:58,780
People now say

513
00:27:59,460 --> 00:28:01,060
I'm successful,

514
00:28:01,380 --> 00:28:03,260
a good chef.

515
00:28:05,780 --> 00:28:07,540
So, it doesn't matter where Hua Su is.

516
00:28:08,220 --> 00:28:09,500
I can do it on my own.

517
00:28:12,900 --> 00:28:13,780
I think

518
00:28:14,220 --> 00:28:15,980
if my dad knew

519
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:18,540
I was like this now,

520
00:28:19,380 --> 00:28:20,900
he'd be happy.

521
00:28:29,220 --> 00:28:30,820
You have a good father.

522
00:28:35,100 --> 00:28:36,900
Where is the new location?

523
00:28:38,060 --> 00:28:39,020
After I leave the hospital,

524
00:28:40,060 --> 00:28:41,100
take me to try it.

525
00:28:42,300 --> 00:28:43,140
Alright,

526
00:28:43,820 --> 00:28:46,260
it's a deal.

527
00:28:48,540 --> 00:28:49,380
Deal.

528
00:28:50,340 --> 00:28:52,420
(Hua Su)
Hua Su's open today!

529
00:28:52,420 --> 00:28:53,260
Well

530
00:28:53,270 --> 00:28:54,280
- excuse me.
- No.

531
00:28:54,300 --> 00:28:55,540
- Hello, we're open...
- Okay, let me see.

532
00:28:56,220 --> 00:28:57,860
We just opened,

533
00:28:57,860 --> 00:28:59,020
would you like to have some lunch?

534
00:28:59,020 --> 00:29:01,020
Sir, would you like to take your wife...

535
00:29:02,340 --> 00:29:03,460
Hua Su just opened.

536
00:29:08,580 --> 00:29:09,420
It's fine.

537
00:29:21,660 --> 00:29:23,540
Let's call it a day.

538
00:29:25,380 --> 00:29:27,020
Wait, it's not yet time.

539
00:29:27,300 --> 00:29:29,180
(Hua Su)
Anyway, no one is coming,

540
00:29:30,140 --> 00:29:32,060
so let's just go home and rest.

541
00:29:38,100 --> 00:29:38,940
Go home.

542
00:29:39,220 --> 00:29:44,340
(Hua Su Restaurant, come inside.
Grand Opening)

543
00:29:44,340 --> 00:29:45,180
Fang Meng,

544
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:47,620
you haven't even
made a single dish yet.

545
00:29:48,140 --> 00:29:50,700
No one has ordered anything.

546
00:29:54,540 --> 00:29:55,380
Well,

547
00:29:55,700 --> 00:29:57,340
don't you know what presentation is?

548
00:29:59,180 --> 00:30:00,820
Don't you know what presentation is?

549
00:30:01,900 --> 00:30:02,740
What?

550
00:30:03,540 --> 00:30:04,940
Just make a few dishes

551
00:30:04,940 --> 00:30:06,460
and display them to people.

552
00:30:06,460 --> 00:30:08,460
Maybe they'll want
to try them after seeing them.

553
00:30:10,050 --> 00:30:11,660
But I don't want to cook.

554
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:14,060
Meng, why are you different now?

555
00:30:14,200 --> 00:30:16,140
Before, you insisted on cooking
when you were not allowed to,

556
00:30:16,380 --> 00:30:18,180
yet now you don't want to?

557
00:30:18,740 --> 00:30:20,140
I'm really tired today.

558
00:30:20,140 --> 00:30:21,300
I don't want to cook.

559
00:30:22,420 --> 00:30:24,420
If you want to do it, go ahead.

560
00:30:27,180 --> 00:30:28,900
Fine, I'll cook.

561
00:30:30,780 --> 00:30:31,660
You're going to cook?

562
00:30:33,620 --> 00:30:34,460
Who?

563
00:30:34,700 --> 00:30:35,620
You're going to cook?

564
00:30:36,780 --> 00:30:37,620
I...

565
00:30:37,900 --> 00:30:38,820
I guess you're right,

566
00:30:39,340 --> 00:30:41,260
it was you who taught me to cook.

567
00:30:41,660 --> 00:30:43,300
How about you try

568
00:30:43,300 --> 00:30:44,860
making a few dishes first?

569
00:30:45,460 --> 00:30:47,460
If it works,

570
00:30:48,300 --> 00:30:49,500
I'll do the rest.

571
00:30:54,220 --> 00:30:55,060
Alright,

